<br>
The only trick to getting the correct version of GrimRot to spawn is to kill the PH at the correct time. If you want the live version to spawn...kill the PH at night so the repop will happen during the day. If you want the Undead version...then kill the PH during the day blah blah blah. The repop will happen between 3 hrs and 3.5 hrs after you kill the PH.<br>
<br>
I was in the same situation as you except I needed the Undead version so I killed the PH at 3,4,5,6,7,8, and 9 am. After 10 million PlaceHolders I finally got the Undead version to spawn. There is no trick to it....just luck of the draw as to wether GrimRot will spawn (provided you killed the PH at the correct time).<br>
<br>
It is a nice item if you can ever get it. In fact I am wearing it now for the Wis it provides. I find myself using a lot of mana in XP groups now. I am usually the main tank and do a LOT of stunning, Yaulping, etc.<br>
<br>
Hope that helps.<br>
<br>
Harrison Abbeyroad 56 Pally Prexus<br>
<br>
